    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a small dent on the rear passenger door, and fading clear coat on the roof. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will soon be due for some routine suspension work and the interior upholstery shows significant wear. It\u2019s an honest car that has been used regularly, offering dependable transportation for a buyer looking for a budget-friendly option.",
