      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive excellence, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. This vehicle represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a machine in truly immaculate condition. Every detail, from the pristine interior surfaces to the flawless exterior finish, reflects a legacy of meticulous preservation and uncompromising mechanical integrity. For those who demand nothing less than perfection, this offering stands as a testament to peak performance and aesthetic refinement.",
      "price": 48500.0,
